Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.75,0:00:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 还没好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.10,0:00:08.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小小兔好厉害 画的很像呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.68,0:00:10.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿嘿 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.47,0:00:14.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要让我等到什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.32,0:00:17.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,累死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.47,0:00:20.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别乱动 这是明天要交的作业
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.38,0:00:23.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我一直都是这个姿势啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.17,0:00:26.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说请你吃肉包了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.31,0:00:31.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会抓人家的弱点
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.56,0:00:33.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好不要动
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.16,0:00:35.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经画到什么程度啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.82,0:00:37.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.71,0:00:39.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托 你快做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.14,0:00:40.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.70,0:00:46.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你该不会说这个大丑女就是我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.27,0:00:48.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了你还有谁…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.17,0:00:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我觉得画的挺好的…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.67,0:00:55.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可没这么丑！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.82,0:00:57.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没照过镜子吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.39,0:00:59.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
